# OpenBSD makefile for:	transfig
# Version required:	3.2
# Date created:		December 2, 1997
# Whom:			Angelos D. Keromytis
#
# $OpenBSD: Makefile,v 1.3 1998/06/13 23:27:02 marc Exp $
